    title: 'Mindfulness for Children: Cultivating Calm & Emotional Resilience',
    category: 'Mental Health',
    excerpt: 'Discover how mindfulness practices can empower children to develop emotional regulation skills, foster inner calm, and build lasting resilience. A guide for parents.',
    metaDescription: 'Discover how mindfulness practices can empower children to develop emotional regulation skills, foster inner calm, and build lasting resilience. A guide for parents.',
    readTime: 10,
