    title: 'When Anxiety Hides: Spotting Emotional Distress Disguised as Anger in Children',
    category: 'Mental Health',
    excerpt: 'Learn to recognize the subtle signs of anxiety in children when it presents as anger, defiance, or irritability. Understand the root cause of challenging behaviors.',
