    slug: 'building-emotional-intelligence-prevent-anger-pre-teens',
    title: 'Building Emotional Intelligence: Proactive Strategies to Prevent Anger Outbursts in Pre-Teens (Ages 10-12)',
    category: 'Mental Health',
    excerpt: 'Discover proactive strategies to build emotional intelligence in pre-teens (ages 10-12) and effectively prevent anger outbursts before they start. Empower your child with vital coping skills.',
