    title: 'Conquering FOMO: Essential Skills to Resist Peer Pressure and Protect Your Mental Wellbeing',
    category: 'Mental Health',
    excerpt: 'Learn essential skills to conquer FOMO, resist peer pressure, and protect your mental wellbeing. Discover strategies for authentic choices & lasting resilience.',
